# Canonical domain: bounce the bare *.pages.dev project URL to the pretty custom
# domain so guests (and QR codes) never see wedding-site-8nh.pages.dev. Only the
# exact production host matches — preview/branch deploys (hash.<project>.pages.dev)
# are left alone. Path + query are preserved via :splat.
https://wedding-site-8nh.pages.dev/*  https://demo.celebrately.us/:splat  302

# SPA fallback: serve the app for any path so history-routed deep links
# (/home, /admin, /rsvp, …) work. Static assets are served before this rule.
/*  /index.html  200
